Package com.assignment.pages

Class BasePage

java.lang.Object
com.assignment.pages.BasePage
Direct Known Subclasses:
DressPage, HomePage, SearchPage
public class BasePage
extends java.lang.Object
Acts as a parent class for all the web pages in this framework. All the web page classes need to extend this class. This class is responsible for locating WebElements by the given WaitStrategy and performing given operations Base Page common to all the web pages for locating WebElements
Author:
Manpreet Kaur M 22-Jun-2021
